      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and a refined presence. It exhibits consistent mechanical maintenance and a well-preserved interior, ensuring a seamless transition to its next proprietor. Rigorously evaluated to meet our dealership's exacting standards, this unit offers an optimal balance of performance and long-term value.",
