    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis remains a benchmark of Japanese engineering, powered by the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. The power delivery is smooth across the rev range, managed by a precise five-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry features the original double-wishbone setup, maintaining the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full cooling system refresh and inspection of the vacuum solenoid 'rat's nest' to ensure boost threshold consistency. A mechanically sound, driver-spec example that prioritizes performance and handling dynamics.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
