    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-maintained and serves as a reliable, stylish daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor stone chips typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and pristine, featuring leather upholstery that remains supple and an infotainment system that functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound; I have stayed ahead of every service interval, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, comfortable ride. This is a solid, honest car that has been cared for by a detail-oriented owner and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 36500.0,
