    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty handles it all with a smile. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to a home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much as I have. Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it!",
