      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-focused example is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically sound, the dual-VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a critical point for this chassis\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The suspension maintains its composure with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis remains communicative and balanced. While the exterior shows minor signs of spirited use consistent with its age, the car remains structurally robust and performance-ready. Ideal for the purist seeking a visceral, high-revving analog experience.",
